programme.desc: Part 2. Terry Denmon breaks from the Louisiana heat to the waterfowl-friendly country of Argentina for a week of pure duck hunting paradise.(n)

programme.title: The Honey Brake Experience
programme.desc: Join the guides at Honey Brake Lodge for a memorable hunt. It's the Bring Avery Home Sweepstakes. Flying ducks and dogs retrieving. It's all about the Honey Brake experience.(n)

programme.title: Easton Bowhunting TV
programme.desc: Michele takes her largest whitetail ever in Oklahoma and Fred takes a Colorado whitetail on their farm with his recurve.(n)

programme.title: Old School Outdoors
programme.desc: Greg Hall heads to the Double G to try his hand at finding a buck that trips his trigger. Along the way, he experiences one of the greatest days in the field.(n)

programme.title: Big Boys TV
programme.desc: Finally, Kevin and Jada have drawn Iowa archery tags. Follow them as they are on pursuit for the big boy.(n)

programme.title: Country Boys Outdoors

programme.title: On The Road With Rock & Aaron
programme.desc: Aaron is in Indiana hunting whitetails, but let's his judgement get the best of him.(n)

programme.title: Project Mule Deer *
programme.desc: During the last three decades, we've seen an alarming decrease in mule deer populations across the west. We follow the mule deer of North America through the seasons and discuss the issues that mule deer are facing today.(n)
